channel.title: Frankie
channel.desc: Romance 2019 Facing a terminal illness, acclaimed actress Frankie arranges a trip for her loved ones to Sintra, Portugal. Yet, despite the city's allure, the journey proves ineffective in bridging the widening divides among them. Ira Sachs , Ira Sachs , Mauricio Zacharias, Isabelle Huppert, Sennia Nanua, Ariyon Bakare, Jeremie Renier, Brendan Gleeson, Marisa Tomei, Greg Kinnear, Ira Sachs, Ira Sachs.
